subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: The sixth-seeded Bears denied the third-seeded Bluejays a trip to the West Region semifinals, with alley-oops, powerful putbacks and an impressive 11 baskets from long distance.
